skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: starlink tracker
des:
Starlink Tracker will tell you the next visible pass of Starlink for today, from your location.
If there is no visible pass for the current day, it will tell you so.

When you invoke it for the first time it will ask you for your position (latitude and longitude).
You can easily get them by googling "my gps coordinates".
For example, Miami's position is: Latitude: -80.1917902 Longitude: 25.7616798
Your position will be maintained, so you will not be prompted every time you invoke the skill.

You can change your geolocation at any time by saying "set position"
You can verify your geolocation by saying "get position"
You can request the next visible pass by saying "next pass"
